text.section:
The request for final disposition required under subsection (b) of this section shall be accompanied by a statement from the managing official having immediate supervision over the inmate setting forth:
the inmate's term of confinement;
the time already served;
the time remaining to be served;
the amount of diminution credits awarded for good conduct;
the date of parole eligibility for the inmate; and
the most recent decision of the Maryland Parole Commission or the Board of Review of the Patuxent Institution relating to the inmate.
